apiResult.english: I was not capable of stopping it even while using both hands. That surprised me a little. Was that your full power? Well, it seems to be... disappointing.
apiResult.indo: Saya tidak mampu menghentikannya bahkan saat menggunakan kedua tangan. Itu membuatku sedikit terkejut. Apakah itu kekuatan penuh Anda? Yah, sepertinya... mengecewakan.
